Package com.intellij.xdebugger.frame

Class XStackFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.xdebugger.frame.XValueContainer
      • com.intellij.xdebugger.frame.XStackFrame
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JavaStackFrame, PyStackFrame, StackFrameItem.CapturedStackFrame, XsltStackFrame

    public abstract class XStackFrame
extends XValueContainer
    Represents a frame of execution stack. The selected frame is shown in 'Variables' panel of 'Debug' tool window. Override XValueContainer.computeChildren(com.intellij.xdebugger.frame.XCompositeNode) to show local variable, parameters, fields available in the frame

      • getEqualityObject

        public java.lang.Object getEqualityObject()
        If stack frame is not changed after step expanded nodes and selection will be restored in 'Variables' tree. A stack frame is assumed unchanged if this method return equal non-null values before and after step
        Returns:
        an object which will be used to determine if stack frame changed after step
